It occurs to me that another way we could win with this user-header stuff
is to use the ";" convention for the request file. eg,

    FROM-PROGRAM:KMP (by hand)
    FROM-XUNAME:KMP
    FROM-UNAME:KMP
    HEADER-FORCE:RFC733
    AUTHOR:KMP
    RCPT:(KMP @MC)
