change "USER-HEADER:..." to "USER-HEADER;nnn<return>..." as well as
"SUBJECT:..." to "SUBJECT;nnn<return>...".

I will probably do this myself one of these days. I note it here on
BUG-BABYL so if someone gets ambitious they can try to beat me to it.

