^V[BABYL.LEVITT and only deletes it when the babyl file has been updated
on disk.

[BABYL.LEVITT is 1173 *pages* long.  Not even bare emacs can read a file
that big, and neither can MM.  There are two things you can do (assuming
you're not a Teco wizard):
